text: Xavier Zequeira (2 May 1907 - 10 September 1976) was a Puerto Rican sports shooter. He competed in the trap event at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1907 births Category:1976 deaths Category:People from Loíza, Puerto Rico Category:Puerto Rican male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Puerto Rico Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics
